Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 06 of Thoracic CT
When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'I describe' radio button is enabled and preselected
And 'I know' radio button is enabled
And 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Localization' tab is enabled and preselected
And 'Characterization' tab is enabled
And 'Differential diagnosis' tab is enabled

And 'Nodular' radio button is enabled
And 'Reticular' radio button is enabled
And 'Increased parenchymal density' radio button is enabled
And 'Decreased parenchymal density' radio button is enabled

And 'Diffuse' radio button is enabled
And 'Basal' radio button is enabled
And 'Apical' radio button is enabled
And 'Focal' radio button is enabled
And a single selection localizer is enabled

And 'Subpleural' radio button is enabled
And 'Bronchocentric' radio button is enabled
And 'Diffuse' radio button is enabled
And 'Substantial exclusion of extrapleural space (EPS)' radio button is enabled

And 'Symmetrical' radio button is enabled
And 'Asymmetrical' radio button is enabled


When I select 'Focal' radio button
Then 'Symmetrical' radio button is disabled
And 'Asymmetrical' radio button is disabled

When I select 'Asymmetrical' radio button
Then 'Right' radio button is disabled
And 'Left' radio button is disabled
